      "sc:description": "VariantFoldRNA is a Snakemake pipeline for predicting SNPs that alter RNA structure (riboSNitches) transcriptome-wide. It is a flexible, containerized pipeline that automates the installation of dependencies and allows customization for specific research questions.",
